Creating Custom Chatbot using Lambda function!


1. First write the Lambda Function to access the input from chat bot. (Lambda function is done under AWS Lambda using Note.js code)

2. Create the custom chatbot via AWS Lex console.

3. Create the custom Intent for desired bot.

4. Provide the intent with custom slot.

5. Add the Sample utterances for user input. 

6. Define the slot and their question?

7. Link the custom chatbot with Lambda function.

8. And then build it and test it. 


Done!!!!!!!!!!


Publish a Version and Create an Alias

Only publish version can connect the outside world.

Before publishing we have to set the alias that user can understand.

